name: Chicken El Toro
description:
Chicken El Toro - Highly addictive gameplay

Left in the bottom of a city filled with obstacles like cars and lakes, can you make it out? And can you beat your highscore?

Use the chickens extraordinary jumping powers to navigate across roads filled with cars and lakes with floating barrels and make the highest possible score to make it out.

Actual Gameplay

Navigation Controls

Navigate with a+w+d keys and mouse.

Oculus Rift Support is coming in the near future!

Supported platforms
  • Windows
  • Mac

This is a BETA game and bugs and updates are added continuously.
